translated:
Yngwe, Sven Ture Konrad, parish priest, Valdemarsvik, born on 15/3/02 in Fivelstad, Östergötland. Son of Sven Y. and Ida Ljungquist. Married on 31 with Brita Gjörling. Children: Ulla and Kerstin born in 31, Sven in 33, Mats in 39. 

Education: graduated from Lund in 22, theological philosophy degree in 25, theology candidate in 30, practical theological examination and ordained as a priest from the Linköping Diocese in 31. 

Worked as a pastor in Västra Ny in 31, in Vireda in 32, as a pastor at the central prison in Mariestad the same year, as a deputy pastor in Adelöv in 34, appointed parish priest there in 35, and finally served in Valdemarsvik from 44. 

In Adelöv, served as the chairman of the church assembly from 35-44, municipal representative from 39-44, municipal council member in 44, and school board member from 35-44. 

In Valdemarsvik, served as the chairman of the church council from 44, school board member from 45, child welfare board member from 44, member of lecture associations and library board from 44, and in the Valdemarsvik diocese home.
